inputFiles.geometry.gdml:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no" ?>
<gdml xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="http://cern.ch/service-spi/app/releases/GDML/schema/gdml.xsd">
  <define/>
  <materials>
    <material name="BlackHole" state="solid">
      <T unit="K" value="293.15"/>
      <MEE unit="eV" value="823"/>
      <D unit="g/cm3" value="1e+8"/>
      <fraction n="1" ref="G4_Pb"/>
    </material>
  </materials>
  <solids>
    <tube name="solidWaterPhantomCylinder" rmin="0" rmax="50" z="200" startphi="0" deltaphi="360" aunit="deg" lunit="mm"/>
    <tube name="solidVacuumCylinder" rmin="0" rmax="55" z="220" startphi="0" deltaphi="360" aunit="deg" lunit="mm"/>
    <tube name="solidWorld" rmin="0" rmax="60" z="240" startphi="0" deltaphi="360" aunit="deg" lunit="mm"/>
  </solids>
  <structure>
    <volume name="logicWaterPhantomCylinder">
      <materialref ref="G4_WATER"/>
      <solidref ref="solidWaterPhantomCylinder"/>
    </volume>
    <volume name="logicVacuumCylinder">
      <materialref ref="G4_Galactic"/>
      <solidref ref="solidVacuumCylinder"/>
      <physvol copynumber="1" name="physWaterPhantomCylinder">
        <volumeref ref="logicWaterPhantomCylinder"/>
        <position name="physWaterPhantomCylinder_pos" unit="mm" x="0" y="0" z="-5"/>
      </physvol>
    </volume>
    <volume name="logicWorld">
      <materialref ref="BlackHole"/>
      <solidref ref="solidWorld"/>
      <physvol copynumber="1" name="physVacuumCylinder">
        <volumeref ref="logicVacuumCylinder"/>
      </physvol>
    </volume>
  </structure>
  <setup name="Default" version="1.0">
    <world ref="logicWorld"/>
  </setup>
</gdml>
inputFiles.run.mac:
/run/initialize

##########################################
####### Particle Source definition #######
##########################################

/gps/verbose 0
/gps/particle proton
/gps/position 0 0 -10.5 cm
/gps/pos/type Beam
/gps/direction 0 0 1
/gps/ene/type Gauss
/gps/ene/mono 150 MeV
/gps/ene/sigma 1.5 MeV
/gps/ene/max 1000 MeV
/gps/ene/min 0 MeV

##########################################
################ Scoring #################
##########################################

/score/create/cylinderMesh CylZ_Mesh
/score/mesh/translate/xyz 0 0 -0.5 cm
/score/mesh/cylinderSize 5 10.0 cm
/score/mesh/nBin 1 400 1
/score/quantity/energyDeposit eDep
/score/filter/particle protonFilter proton
/score/quantity/cellFlux fluence
/score/filter/particle protonFilter proton
/score/close

/score/create/boxMesh YZ_Mesh
/score/mesh/translate/xyz 0 0 -0.5 cm
/score/mesh/boxSize 0.25 2.0 10.0 cm
/score/mesh/nBin 1 80 100
/score/quantity/energyDeposit eDep
/score/filter/particle protonFilter proton
/score/quantity/cellFlux fluence
/score/filter/particle protonFilter proton
/score/close

/score/create/probe EntrySlab 2.5 cm
/score/probe/locate 0 0 -10.55 cm
/score/quantity/cellFlux fluxdiff
/score/filter/particle protonFilter proton
/score/close

/analysis/h1/create fluxdiff_0 fluxdiff_differential_0 100 0 200 MeV none linear
/score/fill1D 0 EntrySlab fluxdiff

##########################################
################## Run ###################
##########################################

/run/beamOn 1000

##########################################
############ Collect results #############
##########################################

/score/dumpQuantityToFile CylZ_Mesh eDep CylZ_Mesh_eDep.txt
/score/dumpQuantityToFile CylZ_Mesh fluence CylZ_Mesh_fluence.txt
/score/dumpQuantityToFile YZ_Mesh eDep YZ_Mesh_eDep.txt
/score/dumpQuantityToFile YZ_Mesh fluence YZ_Mesh_fluence.txt
/score/dumpQuantityToFile EntrySlab fluxdiff EntrySlab_fluxdiff.txt

project.title: Proton pencil beam in water
project.description:
Proton pencil beam with initial kinetic energy 150 MeV and 1% energy spread.
The target is a cylindrical water phantom with a radius of 10 cm and a length of 20 cm.

We score dose from all particles and fluence according to primary particles (protons), secondary protons, and all protons.
